commit.message: Allow overriding device names for hard drive directories
Improved MIDI configuration, device helper update
Disable previous sdl patch, disable mfi instead (macos)
Add SDL patch to fix input monitoring security warning in macOS
Properly iterate over SDL displays and modes
Fall back to -lOpenGL if -lGL is not found
Remove direct dependency on X11 (for now)
Device helper is updated for hotplug functionality in the Launcher
